==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trumpetwood
<hw>Trump"et*wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A tropical American tree (<spn>Cecropia peltata</spn>) of the
Breadfruit family, having hollow stems, which are used for wind
instruments; -- called also <altname>snakewood</altname>, and
<altname>trumpet tree</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trumpie</ent>⟦br⟧
